COMMON STOCK DIVIDENDS

THE QUARTERLY COMMON STOCK DIVIDEND WAS INCREASED BY 11.1 PERCENT IN APRIL 2012 TO $0.90 PER COMMON SHARE, MAKING 2012 THE 25TH CONSECUTIVE YEAR THAT THE COMPANY INCREASED ITS ANNUAL DIVIDEND PAYMENT.

COMMON STOCK REPURCHASE PROGRAM

THE COMPANY PURCHASED $5.0 BILLION OF ITS COMMON STOCK IN 2012 UNDER ITS SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAM. THE PROGRAM BEGAN IN 2010 AND HAS NO SET TERM OR MONETARY LIMITS.

